race.comment: The $200,000 Listed Nudgee Stakes. MIDNIGHT IN TOKYO (2) has put back-to-back Listed wins together and is racing high on confidence this preparation. Maloney has been on board for both those victories and stays in the saddle here. Can continue the rich vein of form. DANCE TO THE BOOM (1) strung three wins together on the bounce before being given a bit of a freshen up from in-form conditioner Bjorn Baker. Drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley and rates among the leading hopes. The well-related SUNSET DREAMING (9) (half to G1 winner Benedetta) will be ready to peak now fourth-up from the break and must be respected from the Gollan yard. Genuine top-three candidate. LONHRO'S QUEEN (7) is a bit hit or miss but is more than capable enough on her day. In the mix if she brings her A-game. NAVYONTHEHIGHWAY (5) makes some appeal despite the wide draw.
